{"id":211707,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":1,"day":17}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"磁力","column":"","genre":"","count":"250","ytitle":"","mtitle":"妖魔，你逃不了!","ftitle":"","authors":["福林"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"福林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妖魔，我们认得你!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汉奸、强盗、杀人犯三位一体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尾巴上挂着青面獠牙旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躲在壁角落里嘁嘁嚓嚓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是谁一不留神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就给你窜出来咬一口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妖魔，你逃不了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的一本账在我们手里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水缸里你放过毒药，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"街头上你造过谣言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的手上一股血腥味，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的鼻子喷出的尽是臭气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妖魔，你逃不了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那怕你变成和尚道士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那怕你变成神仙皇帝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者是白面书生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者是红唇美女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是你的尾巴变不了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一看，就是个畜牲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清明世界，朗朗乾坤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不容你这畜牲横行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民摆下了天罗地网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你只有跪下来投降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如若再敢顽抗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就送你去见阎王。"}]}